  "text": "where ρ n , ρ i , and ρ b are the energy densities of neutral hydrogen, ionized hydrogen, and the total baryons, respectively, and γ is the coupling between the ionized and neutral component given by γ ≃ σv H + ,H /(2m H ), where σv H + ,H = 0.649 T 0.375 × 10 −9 cm 3 s −1 [CITATION_1] .",
